title: Jimmy Butler dishes no-look assist
text:
It’s only the preseason, but Jimmy Butler looks like he’s in midseason form.
Butler dished this no-look pass to Nikola Mirotić during tonight’s game against the Nuggets in Denver.
#PointJimmy https://t.co/kLDjjsN87A
— Ricky O'Donnell (@SBN_Ricky) October 9, 2015
Butler has six points in 19 minutes – including this and-one lay-in.
"Why can't Jimmy Butler be MVP?" – D. Rose https://t.co/io1H70e0Ft
— Ricky O'Donnell (@SBN_Ricky) October 9, 2015
Jimmy Butler says he loves having Derrick Rose as a teammate Chicago trails 57-34 at the half.
Jimmy Butler assuming bigger leadership role for Bulls – By Sam Smith | 10.8.2015 | 9:30 a.m. http://t.co/RfR2aL4XrD
— Dennis Rodman (@dennisrodman) October 9, 2015
